column2: "Ah <%me>. I have not seen you in a while."
"Me? I'm injured, but there is no need for your concern."
"If you're looking for Master Gettemhart, then he is up ahead."
"Even though I'm his companion? Are you making fun of me?"
"I have no qualification to have any association with Master Gettemhart."
"... please forget what I said just now."
"...<%me>, if you would ignore me and continue on your way."
